headline: GTA Online
subtitle: TRY HARD NOT TO DIE
content: If bringing down two criminal masterminds in a towering high-rise just in time to spend the holidays with your loved ones is on your festive list, good news! Now you can live out your bloody festive fantasy and receive the WM 29 Pistol for your trouble. Word is, there’s been some suspicious activity around the Weazel Plaza Apartments…
